divs: sighting detailsbetween 19:30 and 19:40 ish, i was travelling along the a54 chester road, south of marton, just after the last roundabout as you leave winsford. on my right handside was a pair of fairly large 'square' lights, with the distance of a 'square' between them. it seemed to be hovering, it was there for about 15-20 seconds (i was driving at the time). then either, lose height or move away (this, i only caught a glimpse as the hedges turn into trees further up the road. although heading into dusk it was still relatively light. ...mmm... regards maybe be related to this incident >>> http:\\www.zimbio.com\ufos\articles\378\ufo+sighting+over+cheshire+4th+september+2008
